videos.description: Devonte Green inbounds the ball to a cutting Romeo Langford, who rises up for the rim-rocking two-handed slam, extending Indiana's first-half lead.
videos.headline: Green hits Langford for huge two-handed jam

videos.description: Romeo Langford pushes in transition and sends a pass to the rim, where Juwan Morgan elevates for the two-handed alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Langford lobs to Morgan for alley-oop flush
